          All Products
        </h2>
        <button className='border-2 rounded-full py-1 px-2 border-red-400 text-red-400 hover:bg-red-500 hover:text-white transistion-all ' onClick={()=>setUploadProduct(true)}>Upload Products</button>
      </div>
